    • getSyncedCustomRegistries

      public static Set<ResourceKey<? extends Registry<?>>> getSyncedCustomRegistries()
      返回 An unmodifiable view of the set of synced non-vanilla datapack registry IDs。 Clients must have each of a server's synced datapack registries to be able to connect to that server; vanilla clients therefore cannot connect if this list is non-empty on the server.
      返回:
      An unmodifiable view of the set of synced non-vanilla datapack registry IDs
